<div id="container">
    <main>
        <section id="hero">
            <h1>Welcome to SHAPeS Page!</h1>
            <p class="tagline">
                This is where I like to write what's on my mind, I also link to
                cool (to me) projects I'm working on! You can see my blog posts
                up in the corner of the screen, as well as services and info on
                the site.
            </p>
